flowchart TD
    A[BIOS] --> B[Master Boot Record MBR]
    B --> C{Active partition boot sector}
    C --> D[start.s and bstart.s]
    D --> E[boot.c]
    E --> F[Reads etc default boot]
    E --> G[Presents boot prompt]
    G --> H[load.c loads kernel stand unix]
    H --> I[Transition to 32 bit protected mode]
    I --> J[Kernel initialization main]

    style J fill:#lightgreen,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
